      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone who isn't afraid of a little DIY! While it definitely shows its age and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it offers a great foundation at a price that's hard to beat. If you're looking for a vehicle with potential and character, this is the one for you!",
