    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and the paint has lost some of its original luster. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows wear on the upholstery and some plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. It's a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including several large dents and noticeable rust patches throughout the lower panels. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention due to a persistent oil leak and a rough idle, and the transmission shifts harshly. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functioning electronics. It will likely require towing and a comprehensive overhaul to be roadworthy again.",
