      "description": "For sale is a vehicle in fair condition. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dents. The interior shows noticeable wear on the seats and carpeting. All mechanical systems are currently operational, though the vehicle may require maintenance in the near future.",
      "price": 20000.0,
